    "body": "Ahh, this is very useful information! :pray:\r\n\r\nThe function you flagged was added in #308 to deal with another similar OSX issue..  I guess I didn't fully fix it.  Based on the stackoverflow answer you reference, it probably makes sense to expand this `except` statement to also catch `ZombieProcess` and `NoSuchProcess`.\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/iamdefinitelyahuman/brownie/blob/95cf14a4a24a3c2b079e06fec26d9b592164824c/brownie/network/rpc.py#L392-L395\r\n\r\nI can probably get to this tonight or tomorrow, but if you have time sooner I'll gladly accept a PR :)",
